####### Hibernate Features ######
1. Auto DDL
2. HQL
3. Cache Support
4. Primary Key Generator
5. Validations
6. Exception free. All are runtime exceptions
7. ORM support ... Object Stuctures
8. OGM - Object Graph Mapping
9. Search
10. Annotations Support
11. Inbuilt connection pool support


######### Required Steps ######
1. POJO class
2. Mapping file  -- ex:., student.hbm.xml
3. Configuration file  --- Default name is : hibernate.cfg.xml
    DTD
    <hibernate-configuration>
        DB Driver properties
        DB connection pool properties
        Hibernate commands
        Attach mapping files
    </hibernate-configuration>
4. Test classes

######## HQL - Hebernate Query Language #####
Search for .createQuery(